cognitive:
  principle: "The \U0001F9E0\U0001F578Ô∏è\U0001F517 (Associative Memory Network Scaffold) defines the architecture for a dynamic,\
    \ associative memory system. \nIt enables the storage, linking, and context-sensitive retrieval of diverse information\
    \ types (episodic, semantic, \nprocedural) based on relational strength, recency, relevance, and emotional tagging, forming\
    \ a rich, \ninterconnected knowledge web. It supports not just recall but also inference and pattern completion across\
    \ linked concepts.\n"
